    {
      "para_id": "Q001075.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , nominee of Inana , built the Ebgal ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001075.8",
      "line_range": "8",
      "translation": "(i 8) ( When ) he made the E-ana exceed all the mountains for ( Inana ) , then Luma-tur , child of En-ana-tum , fashioned numerous inscribed clay nails , and embellished the E-ana for her with them ."
    }
  ],
